OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FCould the likely changes to STV News
OL,7,Feventually have implications for local
OL,8,Fadvertisers?
OL,10,FIt's a question which has not been
OL,11,Fdiscussed in the row surrounding the
OL,12,Fstation's plans.
OL,14,FOfcom is due to say in the next few
OL,15,Fweeks whether to allow STV to cut the
OL,16,Fseparate service for the old Grampian
OL,17,Fregion.
OL,19,FThe row over this change has been
OL,20,Fintense.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14202
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut STV also wants to cut the two
OL,7,Fcurrent sub-opts ` those for the areas
OL,8,Fserved by the Craigkelly transmitter
OL,9,Fwhich covers Edinburgh and the Angus
OL,10,Ftransmitter near Dundee.
OL,12,FWhatever might happen, there would seem
OL,13,Fto be little chance of a reprieve for
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FThe current proposal ` which Ofcom has
OL,17,Fsaid it is likely to approve ` would
OL,18,Fsee most news output go out across both
OL,19,FSTV's franchise areas.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14203
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut there'd be a 9 minute recorded
OL,7,Fsub-opt for the Grampian area during
OL,8,Fthe 6pm programme.
OL,10,FIn itself, this does not affect STV's
OL,11,Fservice to local advertisers. For about
OL,12,F25 years, it's had 4 micro-regions.
OL,13,FThey match the current news regions but
OL,14,Fpredate them.
OL,16,FSTV has, however, mentioned that it
OL,17,Fhopes to save on distribution costs if
OL,18,Fthe news changes go through.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
