OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FAs the station uses gifted space on
OL,7,FFreeview, this surely refers to
OL,8,Fsatellite distribution.
OL,10,FOnly one of STV's HD regions is on the
OL,11,Fgroup of multiplexes used by ITV 1. Its
OL,12,Fother three regions are on space hired
OL,13,Felsewhere.
OL,15,FIndeed the Dundee and Edinburgh HD
OL,16,Fregions are encrypted. Freesat viewers
OL,17,Fthere get an SD service on channel 103
OL,18,Fto ensure they get the correct local
OL,19,Fnews and ads.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14205
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FWill this be sustainable if Ofcom
OL,7,Fapproves the cuts?
OL,9,FAre two extra HD slots worth it for
OL,10,Fadverts for Paulo's chip shop and the
OL,11,Findependent used tyre specialist? (Well
OL,12,Fmaybe that's unfair to the ultra local
OL,13,Fadvertisers but whenever I've watched
OL,14,Fthey can seem like adverts for the
OL,15,Fsmall shop right opposite the cinema.)
OL,17,FTwo HD streams would seem enough. And
OL,18,Fthey'd probably be enough to satisfy
OL,19,Fall the major Scottish advertisers.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14206
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe SD streams which would be freed up
OL,7,Fcould be used to bring STV + 1 to
OL,8,Fsatellite. It is currently only on
OL,9,Fcable and Freeview.
OL,11,FAnd would the two small advertising
OL,12,Fsub-regions be viable if they were only
OL,13,Fon Freeview?
OL,15,FSTV has said nothing to imply any
OL,16,Fchanges are likely soon. In any case,
OL,17,Fpresumably there are contracts to
OL,18,Fhonour.
OL,20,FBut let's keep an eye on this.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14207
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1772549423
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV news cuts: possible impact
OL,4,Con advertising sub-regions
OL,5,
OL,6,FITV closed some advertising sub-regions
OL,7,Fyears ago. They now align exactly with
OL,8,Fits news regions.
OL,10,FThe world is a very different place too
OL,11,Fto the one which existed when these
OL,12,Fsub-regions were created.
OL,14,FSTV's commitment to advertising
OL,15,Fsub-regions over the years is
OL,16,Fcommendable.
OL,18,FSmall local advertisers have popped up
OL,19,Fin slots during popular network shows.
OL,23,EPub: 01-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
